high_descs: Turn around, head to the counter on the left, left of the stove.
Open the cabinet under the counter, left of the stove, pick up the bowl in the cabinet.
Turn around, bring the bowl to the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge.
Take the chilled bowl out of the fridge, turn left, go to the sink.
Open the left cabinet under the sink, put the chilled bowl in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl in the cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, go ahead, turn left, go to counter between microwave and stove.
Open cabinet under fork, remove bowl in cabinet, close cabinet door.
Open fridge door, put bowl in fridge directly in front of egg, close door.  Wait for short time, open fridge door, and remove bowl.  Shut fridge door.
Turn around, walk to sink, turn right to face sink.
Open left cabinet under sink, put bowl in cabinet, shut door.
anns.task_desc: Get bowl, cool in fridge, put in cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter that is to the left of the stove.
Open the cupboard that is below the counter next to the stove.  Grab the bowl that is in the cupboard.
With the bowl in hand turn round and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge.  Place the bowl in front of the egg that is on the top shelf. Close the door.  Open the door and grab the bowl that is on the top shelf.
With the bowl in hand go to the sink.
Open the cabinet door that is under the sink and on the left side.  Place the bowl in the cabinet and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl away in cabinet.
